description.en:
TED: Unleashing the Crypto Bear-bellion
Hey, all you freakin' troublemakers, outcasts, and meme maniacs out there! If you've got a thing for potty-mouthed teddy bears and a burning desire to mess with the crypto universe, you've hit the jackpot. We're takin' the crazy-ass humour from the movie Ted and mixin' it up with the kickass power of the BNB blockchain to create the most badass meme token you've ever seen: TED!
